<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-1522] Handle logging levels via log4j.xml</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-1522</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We don&apos;t have a properties file to tell log4j what to do, so we inherit other frameworks&apos; settings.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Suggestion is to add a log4j.xml file in a canonical place and set up logging levels, maybe separating out components for ease of setting levels during debugging.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
